		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hey there, i want to convert a spc ripped from a snes rom to midi, i`ve tried w mod2midi but all i got is a empty file.
<br />
<br />It must be the most basic thing to do for you all but im really having a hard time and would really apreciate any help.
<br />
<br />Thank you for your time!

		

